text: Armel Oroko (born 24 December 1980) is a footballer from the Central African Republic. ==Career== Before signing with Sogéa FC in the summer of 2008, Oroko played for AS Tempete Mocaf. ==International career== He is also a member of the Central African Republic national football team.Profile national-soccer- teams.com ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Central African Republic footballers Category:Central African Republic international footballers Category:AS Tempête Mocaf players Category:Expatriate footballers in Gabon Category:Central African Republic expatriate footballers in Gabon Category:Central African Republic expatriate footballers Category:Association footballers not categorized by position
